name: VRGOS Worship & Praise Music
summary: This app was created to spread the good news of the Gospel. With one click you will experience and participate in 360 church service, singing and preaching. Discover new and upcoming recording artist, gospel and Christian music. This app promises to uplift and inspire your day.  If you like Gospel, Worship and Praise Music, take some time out and watch some gifted singers and musicians. Hear some of the greatest preachers expound on God's word.  You will be in the middle of the worship experience right...
